*1996 – Member, Accademia dei Lincei
==Family==
Esaki&#x27;s daughter, Anna Esaki, is married to Craig S. Smith, former Shanghai bureau chief of &quot;The New York Times&quot; and China bureau chief of &quot;The Wall Street Journal&quot;.

