<doc id="217879" wikidata="Q7972225" url="?curid=217879" title="Washington State">
<text>Washington State may refer to:

* Washington (state), a U.S. state, often referred to as &quot;Washington state&quot; to distinguish it from the American capital city, Washington, D.C.
* Washington State University, a land-grant college located in the state of Washington
* Washington State Cougars, the athletic program of Washington State University

